      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BREAKOUT LAD (4) was out the back early but wound up hard to finish in the minors when third (30.08) over 520m at this track. First attempt at the staying journey. Goes very well from this draw with two wins and two minor placings from five starts. Can find winning form. RUPEE'S ROCKET (8) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 4 last run (30.75) at Q Lakeside. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Must be included in calculations. OLIVER GO (2) goes very well this course and distance starting eight times for three wins and three minors. Placed last time (35.12) at this track in a Grade 5/6, finishing third and beaten 5.5 lengths. Looks suited here and can measure up. COOLHAND SUE (1) is right in the mix.",
